snippet.title: Stefanie Lugo - Real Estate Business Coach
snippet.description:
Helping you get control of your real estate business - once and for all. I'm Stefanie Lugo, and I've climbed my way to the Top 1% of REALTORS®. Now, I am your go-to guide in the world of business systems and marketing for real estate agents, team leaders, and brokers in the US and Canada.

timeline.text:
THE ASIAN RANGE BREAKOUT: 2R NQ STRATEGY

When the Asian Range (20:00 - Midnight EST) is broken to the downside there is a 61% chance that the daily will close bearish.

1. The Asian Range broke to the downside giving me my Bias for the day forming a 15 minute Fair Value Gap.

2. Price traded back up to this same FVG after bias confirmed bearish.

3. Placed my Stop at the Old High created during the Asian Range.

4. 2R static target.

The Asian Range breakout is a reliable statistic that you can use to systematically trade NQ before the market even opens.

Based on 1 year of data from Edgeful analytics.
